headline: This Week: Construction spending, Campbell’s Co. earnings, November jobs report
summary: A look at some of the key business events and economic indicators upcoming this week. The Commerce Department releases its latest snapshot of U.S. construction spending Monday. Economists project that spending slipped 0.1% in October from the previous month.
